Figure_title: FIGURE 3. Pharmacokinetic result of enzastaurin: trough concentration of total analytes. Arithmetic mean (solid circles), SD, and individual trough concentrations (lines) of enzastaurin total analytes (enzastaurin and its metabolites) after enzastaurin administered 500 mg once daily (A) or 250 mg twice daily (B) without or with concurrent pemetrexed.
